OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury considered
OL,4,Cresigning over barrister abuse cases
OL,6,FThe Archbishop of Canterbury Justin
OL,7,FWelby considered resigning after a
OL,8,Freport said a British barrister who
OL,9,Fabused more than 100 children and
OL,10,Fyoung men could have been brought to
OL,11,Fjustice a decade ago.
OL,13,FJohn Smyth QC abused a number of
OL,14,Fpupils at Winchester College in the
OL,15,F1970s and 80s.
OL,17,FSmyth chaired the Christian charity,
OL,18,Fthe Iwerne Trust from 1974 to 1982 -
OL,19,Fwhich ran religious holiday camps.
