OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury considered
OL,4,Cresigning over barrister abuse cases
OL,6,FAn independent review has concluded
OL,7,Fthe abuse was covered up within the
OL,8,FChurch of England for years.
OL,10,FSmyth died aged 75 in South Africa in
OL,11,F2018.
OL,13,FThe school said it apologises
OL,14,Funreservedly for its part in their
OL,15,Fterrible experiences.
OL,17,FJustin Welby said he's "deeply sorry"
OL,18,Fthe abuse happened and checks and
OL,19,Fbalances have since been introduced to
OL,20,Fensure the same couldn't happen today.
