OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury considered
OL,4,Cresigning over barrister abuse cases
OL,6,FSmyth, called an "appalling abuser of
OL,7,Fchildren and young men" in the review,
OL,8,Fabused as many as 130 boys and young
OL,9,Fmen in the UK and Africa over five
OL,10,Fdecades.
OL,12,FHe is said to have subjected his
OL,13,Fvictims to traumatic physical, sexual,
OL,14,Fpsychological and spiritual attacks.
OL,16,FMr Welby also said he donated money to
OL,17,FSmyth on missions in Zimbabwe.
