OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury considered
OL,4,Cresigning over barrister abuse cases
OL,6,FSmyth was able to move to Africa from
OL,7,FEngland while "church officers knew of
OL,8,Fthe abuse and failed to take the steps
OL,9,Fnecessary to prevent further abuse
OL,10,Foccurring", the report said.
OL,12,FMr Welby told Channel 4 News: "Lots of
OL,13,Fpeople funded his mission out there
OL,14,F(in Zimbabwe). I think on two separate
OL,15,Foccasions I gave #40 or #50."
OL,17,FMark Stibbe, a survivor of Smyth's
OL,18,Fabuse, said the abuse had been covered
OL,19,Fup by people "at the highest level of
OL,20,Fthe Church of England".
