OL,6,F"It is very distressing," he said.
OL,8,FDespite Smyth's actions having been
OL,9,Fidentified in the 1980s, the report
OL,10,Fconcluded he was never fully exposed
OL,11,Fand was therefore able to continue his
OL,12,Fabuse.
OL,14,FThe Church has said it is "deeply
OL,15,Fsorry for the horrific abuse" and
OL,16,Fadded that "there is never a place for
OL,17,Fcovering up abuse".
