OL,6,FIt said "had that been done, on the
OL,7,Fbalance of probabilities" Smyth could
OL,8,Fhave been brought to justice "at a
OL,9,Fmuch earlier point" than the Hampshire
OL,10,FPolice investigation in early 2017.
OL,12,FThe review, commissioned a year after
OL,13,FSmyth's death by the Archbishops'
OL,14,FCouncil of the Church of England,
OL,15,Fadded: "Opportunities to establish
OL,16,Fwhether he continued to pose an
OL,17,Fabusive threat in South Africa were
OL,18,Fmissed because of these inactions by
OL,19,Fsenior church officers."
