OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury considered
OL,4,Cresigning over barrister abuse cases
OL,6,FIn a statement, Mr Welby said he was
OL,7,F"deeply sorry that this abuse
OL,8,Fhappened" and "sorry that concealment
OL,9,Fby many people who were fully aware of
OL,10,Fthe abuse over many years meant that
OL,11,FJohn Smyth was able to abuse overseas
OL,12,Fand died before he ever faced justice".
OL,14,FHe added: "I had no idea or suspicion
OL,15,Fof this abuse before 2013.
OL,17,F"Nevertheless the review is clear that
OL,18,FI personally failed to ensure that
OL,19,Fafter disclosure in 2013 the awful
OL,20,Ftragedy was energetically investigated.
