OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury considered
OL,4,Cresigning over barrister abuse cases
OL,6,FAccording to the report, some 30 boys
OL,7,Fand young men are known to have been
OL,8,Fdirectly physically and
OL,9,Fpsychologically abused in the UK, and
OL,10,Fabout 85 boys and young men physically
OL,11,Fabused in African countries, including
OL,12,FZimbabwe, and the total "likely runs
OL,13,Fmuch higher".
OL,15,FThe review found that an argument had
OL,16,Fbeen made that the abuses were
OL,17,F"examples of over-enthusiastic
OL,18,Fcorporal punishment".
