OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury considered
OL,4,Cresigning over barrister abuse cases
OL,6,FIn a joint statement, the Church of
OL,7,FEngland's lead safeguarding bishop,
OL,8,FJoanne Grenfell, and the national
OL,9,Fdirector of safeguarding, Alexander
OL,10,FKubeyinje, said they are "deeply sorry
OL,11,Ffor the horrific abuse" and its
OL,12,F"lifelong effects".
OL,14,FThey welcomed the report's 27
OL,15,Frecommendations and said they would
OL,16,F"consider them now in detail, noting
OL,17,Fwork already under way".
